{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What's in the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brew your own beer! Buy ingredients and follow recipes or create something new, unique, and possibly not awful.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make the place yours! Add new furniture, change wall decors, buy party games\u2026 And clean up the place once in a while, maybe?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get those star ratings high and maintain your reputation on social media.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have fun with minigames! Arcade machine, dart, pool, and also minigames related to your work.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Up for an extra challenge? Take on special daily tasks for extra profits.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/bp-gifs4.gif?t=1732887165\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Turn a ruin into a _classy_ brewpub</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have you ever wanted to open a pub? Now you can! Give new life to an old run-down brewery that you just inherited. Serve the best (or the worst) beer in town and make a reputation for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/bp-gifs1.gif?t=1732887165\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master the art of brewing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you think that brewing is easy? Well yes, but actually no. Recipes are easy enough to follow, but brewing a perfect beer requires precision and experience. Find out if you have it in you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/bp-gifs2.gif?t=1732887165\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become the #1 brewpub!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your customers happy and your place nice and clean. Create your own beer brands, design your labels, keep your kegs full, and never stop growing. Cheers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Super Beer Dealer Simulator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/cb48ef102e6a1d2e98e5b177cbc9cb0abaa69fa6.jpg"},{"name":"Beer Dealer Simulator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/1ba38edf0f5085e0d2b5817f6b37adf99ee0229d.jpg"},{"name":"Serial Cleaner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/533aa009b39e59fa30da54cb885456af7c27dd3e.jpg"},{"name":"5 out of 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/18e55145036d848e824ee4aaebfff58542de38af.jpg"},{"name":"Oink!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/c5a495051efd3b1f91f570b6b95364240e54de37.jpg"},{"name":"Beer Tycoon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/139c890acc9ef6cceb5a47946fe5831654548338.jpg"},{"name":"Enough is enough!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/6b6291006dd3c5d10ac60aacd741b20e93f9dce4.jpg"},{"name":"Mr. Fancy Pants","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/99574849de0fa83bf5d4c98578c9656e0eb56323.jpg"},{"name":"All those beers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/54ee08c3fb585770b84937c846358e174a25c975.jpg"},{"name":"Bigtime smalltalk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755180/fa01fe164e02b4e64c4111f6548ca6ab82b9713d.jpg"}],"total":18},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset